Analyst Conclusion
-------------------
This incident represents a confirmed malware infection with persistence and potential root-level compromise. Despite the endpoint reporting the threat as cleaned, the existence of a long-running malicious process and autorun configuration indicates that the system was previously compromised for an extended period.

The host was treated as untrusted and required full remediation to ensure no residual attacker presence.
